          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Overall the school is good. I also would like to bring to the notice of school management that many parents including grandparents of school students who commute regularly to drop and pick up the students through g square adjacent road which is not in a very good condition poses danger of skidding as I myself couldn’t drive two wheelers in that damaged road. It would of immense help if school management understands the concern and take action with the help of local municipal authorities as there are many students coming from kannampalayam, Pappampatti, peedampalli are using the same way as their regular path like four times in a day.thank you for understanding.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Bridgewoods International School - Kannampalayam"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Anonymous"
          },
          "datePublished": "2025-12-19",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "We are happy with the teachers for the clarity in the teaching. They are friendly and approachable towards students.\nThe Sports Day was organised well and it was equal to an experienced school's event. The events were quick and the students and teachers put in lots of effort. The events started at the informed time and ended within the mentioned time as the teachers worked with coordination. They motivated and encouraged kindergarten students to keep going and complete the game.\nOverall, we are very happy that our children are going to this school. ",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
