          "reviewBody": "Every child is unique in their character, talent, interests, etc.. The educators in Bridgewoods gives individual attention towards the children, supports their curiosity, groom their knowledge towards their passion. In such a way Bridgewoods is standing unique in parents heart and children minds.",
          "publisher": {
